URL: https://github.com/PMCC-BioinformaticsCore/macpie.git
Description: Macpie is an R package for the integrative analysis of transcriptomic screening data in the context of drug discovery and functional genomics. It enables users to systematically combine gene expression data with chemical descriptors, cell phenotypes, and pathway-level annotations to uncover biologically meaningful patterns and therapeutic insights.
